snippet.title: How to Construct the Circumcenter
snippet.description:
Learn how to construct the circumcenter of a triangle in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring.

0:08 What is the Circumcenter and How to Find It
0:43 Draw 3 Perpendicular Bisectors to the Sides of the Triangle
2:19 Identifying the Circumcenter (Point of Concurrency)
2:50 Draw a Circle Around the Triangle Using the Circumcenter as the Center of the Circle
